  "detailed_description": "<h1>Feature List</h1><p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play over 100 games! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Downloadable wallpapers </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make gameplay simpler with Help and Hint functions!</p></li></ul></p><br><h1>Collector's Edition</h1><p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Includes 8 extra themes </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >18 Downloadable Wallpapers </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full soundtrack and music player </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 more collection room</p></li></ul></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rediscover the thrill of finding \"So Much Stuff\" in this fourth installment! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore beautifully crafted levels, clear diverse scenes, and relish in a multitude of engaging mini-games. Collect charming trinkets to adorn a fresh room in \"So Much Stuff 4: Bits and Bobs.\" </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2589320/extras/a3c32ddda22f582e31ff96c50b927813.poster.avif?t=1729640029\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2589320/extras/a3c32ddda22f582e31ff96c50b927813.webm?t=1729640029\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2589320/extras/a3c32ddda22f582e31ff96c50b927813.mp4?t=1729640029\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2589320/extras/c07695b1179808a4e1611b5d185fb861.poster.avif?t=1729640029\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic